@startuml poc_activity
title OpenSDLC PoC — 파이프라인 액티비티 다이어그램\n(full_spiral.yaml 전체 흐름)

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor #EBF5FB
  BorderColor #2980B9
  DiamondBackgroundColor #FDEBD0
  DiamondBorderColor #E67E22
  ArrowColor #2C3E50
  FontSize 11
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFFDE7
  BorderColor #F9A825
}

start

== Phase 0: 부팅 및 설정 로딩 ==

:CLI 인자 파싱\n(--pipeline, --user-story, --max-iterations, --output);

:config.py 임포트 (자동 실행)
├ load_dotenv() → .env 파일 읽기
├ 경로 설정 (PROJECT_ROOT, ENGINE_DIR, ...)
├ LLM_PROVIDER / MODEL / LLM_MAX_RETRIES 결정
└ LOG_LEVEL / LOG_LLM_IO 설정;

:API 키 유효성 검증;
if (API 키 존재?) then (NO)
  #Pink:exit(1) — API 키 오류;
  stop
else (YES)
endif

== Phase 0-2: 파이프라인 정의 로딩 ==

:load_pipeline_definition(pipeline.yaml)
→ YAML 파싱 → PipelineDefinition (Pydantic);

:run_pipeline() 진입
→ PipelineState 초기화
{user_story, steps_completed=[], latest_artifacts={},
 iteration_count=0, max_iterations=N, pipeline_status="running"};

== Phase 0-3: LangGraph 그래프 빌드 ==

:build_graph_from_definition()
각 step마다:
  1. get_agent(agent_id) → AgentConfig (lru_cache)
  2. build_system_prompt() 8단계 조립
  3. create_agent_node() → node_fn 클로저
  4. graph.add_node(node_id, node_fn);
note right
  **System Prompt 조립 8단계**:
  1. AgentCommon.txt (공통 규칙)
  2. Agent별 프롬프트 (.txt)
  3. 출력 artifact 템플릿
  4. [ValidatorAgent] 5종 참조 템플릿
  5. [step.extra_templates]
  6. Constitution 발췌
  7. [ValidatorAgent] _ADVERSARIAL_MANDATE
  8. [CodeAgent] _CODE_FILE_MANDATE
end note

:엣지 연결
├ ValidatorAgent → 조건부 엣지 (make_validator_router)
└ 그 외 → 단순 엣지;

:graph.compile();

== Phase 1: Requirements Analysis ==

:ReqAgent 실행 — 독립 LLM 호출;
note right
  user_message: User Story (최초)
               또는 이전 UC + fail 사유 (재작업)
  output: UseCaseModelArtifact (YAML)
end note

:UseCaseModelArtifact → latest_artifacts 갱신;

:ValidatorAgent 실행 — 독립 LLM 호출;
note right
  user_message: UC artifact YAML만 전달
  (context 격리: ReqAgent 사고 과정 미포함)
  system_prompt에 _ADVERSARIAL_MANDATE 포함
end note

:ValidationReportArtifact 생성
→ get_validation_result() → "pass" | "warning" | "fail";

if (validation_result?) then (pass)
else (warning or fail)
  :iteration_count++;
  if (iteration_count >= max_iterations?) then (YES)
    #Pink:END — max_retries_exceeded;
    stop
  else (NO: 재작업)
    backward: ReqAgent 재호출\n(재작업 모드: 이전 UC + fail 사유 포함);
  endif
endif

== Phase 2: Test Design ==

:TestAgent 실행 (mode=design) — 독립 LLM 호출;
note right
  user_message: UC artifact YAML
  output: TestDesignArtifact (YAML)
end note

:TestDesignArtifact → latest_artifacts 갱신;

:ValidatorAgent 실행 — TestDesign 검증;

if (validation_result?) then (pass)
else (warning or fail)
  :iteration_count++;
  if (iteration_count >= max_iterations?) then (YES)
    #Pink:END — max_retries_exceeded;
    stop
  else (NO)
    backward: TestAgent 재호출 (mode=design);
  endif
endif

== Phase 3: Implementation ==

:CodeAgent 실행 — 독립 LLM 호출;
note right
  user_message: UC artifact + TestDesign artifact
  max_tokens: 16384
  system_prompt에 _CODE_FILE_MANDATE 포함
  output: ImplementationArtifact (YAML + code_files)
end note

:ImplementationArtifact → latest_artifacts 갱신;

:ValidatorAgent 실행 — Implementation 검증;

if (validation_result?) then (pass)
else (warning or fail)
  :iteration_count++;
  if (iteration_count >= max_iterations?) then (YES)
    #Pink:END — max_retries_exceeded;
    stop
  else (NO)
    backward: CodeAgent 재호출;
  endif
endif

== Phase 4: Test Execution ==

:TestAgent 실행 (mode=execution) — 독립 LLM 호출;
note right
  user_message: TestDesign + Implementation artifact
  output: TestReportArtifact (YAML)
end note

:TestReportArtifact → latest_artifacts 갱신;

:ValidatorAgent 실행 — TestReport 검증;

if (validation_result?) then (pass)
else (warning or fail)
  :iteration_count++;
  if (iteration_count >= max_iterations?) then (YES)
    #Pink:END — max_retries_exceeded;
    stop
  else (NO)
    backward: TestAgent 재호출 (mode=execution);
  endif
endif

== Phase 5: Feedback ==

:CoordAgent 실행 — 독립 LLM 호출;
note right
  user_message: TestReport artifact
  output: FeedbackArtifact (YAML)
end note

:FeedbackArtifact → latest_artifacts 갱신;

== Phase 6: 산출물 저장 ==

:steps_completed → extract_iteration() 기준으로 그룹화;

:output/iteration-N/artifacts/*.yaml 저장
(파일명: {seq:03d}_{artifact_id}.yaml);

:latest_artifacts["ImplementationArtifact"] 에서
code_files 추출 → output/workspace/ 에 코드 파일 저장;

:pipeline_status = "completed";

#LightGreen:파이프라인 정상 완료;

stop

== 예외 경로 ==

note right
  **LLM 내부 retry** (call_llm 내부):
  ① 품질 미달 (min_response_chars): max_retries=2회 즉시 재호출
  ② Rate limit (429): rate_limit_retries=3회, _extract_retry_delay() 대기
  ③ Daily quota 소진: QuotaExhaustedError →
     pipeline_status = "quota_exhausted"
     → partial artifacts 저장 가능
end note

@enduml
